# {{ project_name }} Customisation Guide

## Supervisor behavior

- Update `agents/supervisor/prompts.py` to change orchestration logic.
- Update `agents/supervisor/router.py` to add/remove workers or finish rules.

## Worker behavior

- `agents/workers/worker_one.py`: research strategy and source style.
- `agents/workers/worker_two.py`: writing/synthesis structure.

## Shared state

- `agents/state.py` controls what data flows between supervisor and workers.

## Tools

- Add tools in `tools/` and call them from workers.

## Runtime

- Model/provider settings live in `config.yaml` and `.env`.
- API endpoint lives in `api/routes/agent.py`.
